Though my nation is called "Stratocratic-Anarchy Oceanic Empire", it's not actually 'anarchist' nor 'stratocratic'; not even an "empire". "Stratocratia" is the western half of the Oceanic Mainland.

Catalan civils cheered in victory as European forces were now routed and focusing on a total war defensive effort. Catalonia had returned back to Europe. This time with a vengeance against those who had wronged them. The Burritos continued to support the Catalans with everything they had.

The war continued.
